Titolo: NBA 2K22

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: NBA 2K22 is a 2021 basketball simulation video game developed by Von (NBA). It is the 23rd installment in the NBA 2K franchise and the successor to NBA 2K21. The game was released on September 10, 2021 for Microsoft Windows, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X/S.
The NBA 2K22 Arcade Edition was released for Apple Arcade on October 19, 2021.

Genere: Sports 

Valutazione: 72
